snippet.title: Fashion News: Arab Designers Takeover The Cannes Film Festival Red Carpet
snippet.description:
From Priyanka Chopra, Amber Heard to Aishwarya Rai, Hollywood's biggest names and most promising rising stars arrived at the French Riviera for the 2019 Cannes Film Festival this week. Watch as we round-up the most show-stopping looks by Arab designers that walked the red carpet.

Don't forget to subscribe to our channel, you never miss an episode of Fashion News.
